# Websites where people buy abortion pills

Our research has shown that these websites let people buy abortion pills (often called MTP kits) but do not include any additional support. Anyone can get free medical support for their abortion from the {% inlineLink action={discriminant: "external", value: {url: "https://mahotline.org", showPopup: false}} _language="" %}M+A Hotline{% /inlineLink %}.

